fields.name: Dekoni Audio Blue
fields.description: If you are looking for a fun headphone to listen to, one with further improvement capability and robust enough so you do not have to handle them with white gloves then give the Dekoni Audio Blue a try by all means. Dark V shaped and fun sound signature. Rugged construction. Leagues above the original variant in comfort levels.

fields.name: HIFIMAN Sundara Closed Back Review
fields.description: Is the HIFIMAN Sundara Closed Back better than the original Sundara? Each model has its selling points. The Closed Back seems to be unveiled, but it lacks some low-end grunt which can be easily remedied up to a point. So there is the tradeoff. Very good midrange definition. Excellent isolation levels and very little bleed. Beautiful Beechwood cups
